{"tid":534224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]女學神柴灣撞車 撼燈柱鏟壆釀3傷","createTime":"2018-01-19T14:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T18:20:13.000Z","uid":164771,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"56943f289a76a94b0e60b29b4fb549ce1d41116e","tid":534224,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"中午12時許，一輛掛學牌的中型貨車沿柴灣新業街右轉入柴灣道時，與一輛沿柴灣道向小西灣方向行駛的貨Van相撞。中型貨車繼而失控撞毀馬路中心的燈柱，再滑行撞向路邊石壆始停下。事件中，貨Van車頭亦損毀，現場消息指，學牌中型貨車的女司機及教車師傅，與輕型貨車男司機3人受傷，幸只是輕傷，全部送院治理，警方正調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180119/57728604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57728604&d=bGv%2FDjm0j4UK7CCbfR7dsJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5ac7b662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57728604&h=f39c973a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180119/57728604</a>"},{"pid":"93aac1032d0b6e67eec6f775ece80aa29ca0b417","tid":534224,"uid":7355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"支燈熄埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec46f24b3acd9e73b0572ad7f0b29cb8c1404fb","tid":534224,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教車狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98162d6a5d0e5f4497fc77db58c6977f2a9ee3ea","tid":534224,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"個師傅瞓撚著咗?<br />\n由得架車繼續